---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import CTAButton from '../../../components/CTAButton.astro';
import { COMPANY_INFO } from '../../../utils/constants';

const lang = 'en';
const post = {
  title: 'Refrigerated Truck 2026 Cold Chain: Temperature Controlled Transport',
  slug: 'refrigerated-truck-2026-cold-chain',
  excerpt: 'Finance refrigerated trucks for cold chain logistics. 0% down payment for food and pharmaceutical transport. Temperature controlled delivery.',
  date: '2026-01-09',
  author: 'Ing Heng Credit Team',
  readTime: 6,
  category: 'Specialized Trucks',
  image: '/images/blog/refrigerated-truck-financing.jpg'
};

const keywords = ['refrigerated truck financing', 'cold chain logistics', '0% down payment', 'reefer truck Malaysia', 'temperature control transport'],
  breadcrumbItems = [
  { label: 'Home', href: '/en' },
  { label: 'Blog', href: '/en/blog' },
  { label: post.title, href: `/en/blog/${post.slug}` }
];
---

<BaseLayout title={post.title} description={post.excerpt} lang={lang} keywords={keywords}>
  <Breadcrumbs items={breadcrumbItems} />

  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <header class="mb-8">
      <span class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: #D4A574;">Specialized Trucks</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-2" style="color: #2D1810; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase;">{post.title}</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4">{post.excerpt}</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">
        <span>{post.author}</span>
        <span>•</span>
        <time>{new Date(post.date).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</time>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>{post.readTime} min read</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h2>Refrigerated Truck: Cold Chain Growth</h2>

      <p>Cold chain logistics expanding rapidly. Food delivery increasing. Pharmaceutical transport requiring temperature control. Frozen goods demand rising. One refrigerated truck generates RM35,000-RM65,000 monthly revenue with premium rates.</p>

      <h2>Refrigerated Truck Specifications</h2>

      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Type</th>
            <th>Capacity</th>
            <th>New Price</th>
            <th>Used Price</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>Small Reefer</td>
            <td>3-5 tons</td>
            <td>RM180,000-RM220,000</td>
            <td>RM70,000-RM120,000</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Medium Reefer</td>
            <td>5-10 tons</td>
            <td>RM280,000-RM380,000</td>
            <td>RM120,000-RM180,000</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Large Reefer</td>
            <td>10-15 tons</td>
            <td>RM400,000-RM550,000</td>
            <td>RM180,000-RM260,000</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h2>Cold Chain Applications</h2>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Food:</strong> Frozen meat, seafood, dairy</li>
        <li><strong>Pharmaceutical:</strong> Medicine, vaccines, medical supplies</li>
        <li><strong>Beverages:</strong> Fresh juice, dairy products</li>
        <li><strong>Bakery:</strong> Frozen dough, ingredients</li>
        <li><strong>Florist:</strong> Fresh flowers delivery</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Revenue Potential</h2>

      <p><strong>5-Ton Refrigerated Truck:</strong>
  <br>• Rate: RM2,500-RM4,000 per trip (50% premium over normal)
  <br>• Trips: 15-20 per month
  <br>• Monthly revenue: RM45,000-RM65,000
  <br>• Operating costs: RM25,000 (higher due to refrigeration)
  <br><strong>Net profit: RM20,000-RM40,000 per month</strong></p>

      <h2>Financing with 0% Down</h2>

      <p>Ing Heng Credit:
  <br>• 0% down payment
  <br>• Finance used reefer trucks (any age)
  <br>• Fast approval</p>

      <h2>CNY 2026 Opportunity</h2>

      <p>February 2026:
  <br>• Food delivery: +80% demand
  <br>• Premium rates: +40-60%
  <br>• Monthly revenue: RM70,000-RM95,000</p>

      <div style="background: #F5F0E8; border-left: 4px solid #D4A574; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <h3 style="color: #2D1810; margin-top: 0;">Finance Refrigerated Truck with 0% Down</h3>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Cold chain logistics ready. Approved in 24-48 hours.</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 0;"><strong>Contact:</strong> +60175700889 (WhatsApp) | 03-3324 8899 (Phone)</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t">
      <CTAButton text="Get Refrigerated Truck Financing" link={COMPANY_INFO.whatsapp.link} variant="accent" size="large" />
    </footer>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  h2 { color: #2D1810; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 2rem; margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; border-bottom: 3px solid #D4A574; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  h3 { color: #8B6F47; font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  p { line-height: 1.8; color: #374151; }
  strong { color: #2D1810; font-weight: 700; }
  ul { list-style: none; padding-left: 0; }
  li { padding-left: 1.5rem; position: relative; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #374151; }
  li::before { content: '✓'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #D4A574; font-weight: bold; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1.5rem 0; }
  th { background: #2D1810; color: #F5F0E8; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left; }
  td { border: 1px solid #E5E7EB; padding: 0.75rem; }
  br { display: none; }
</style>
